
{% comment %}
================================================================================
  PRODUCT SHORTS — performance-optimized rewrite
  Same visuals, same functionality, same schema. Facade pattern preserved.

  OPTIMIZATIONS APPLIED (est. saving):
   1. Thumbnails  hqdefault(480x360,~15KB) primary instead of maxresdefault
                  (1280x720,~70KB). YouTube Shorts try oar2.jpg (portrait 9:16)
                  first -> no landscape->portrait crop. ~55KB/thumbnail
                  (~220KB on a 4-up row), plus correct aspect for Shorts.
   2. img attrs   decoding="async", fetchpriority high(first)/low(rest),
                  sizes="(max-width:767px)45vw,(max-width:991px)30vw,22vw".
   3. Preconnect  <link rel=preconnect/dns-prefetch> to i.ytimg.com — warms the
                  thumbnail CDN connection before the imgs request.
   4. CSS once    Shared popup CSS pulled OUT of the per-block {% style %} and
                  injected ONCE per page via window.YTPopupStylesInjected.
                  ~1.5KB CSS de-duplicated for every extra block on the page.
   5. Short IDs   Class/element prefix shortened to avs-{tail} (see note below).
                  ~30-40% smaller class strings, repeated dozens of times.
   6. GPU         will-change:transform on the track; translate3d() everywhere;
                  transition:all -> explicit props on arrows/dots.
   7. JS leaks    Global mousemove/touchmove/mouseup/touchend listeners are now
                  added on dragStart and REMOVED on dragEnd (bound refs). They
                  no longer fire on every pointer event page-wide while idle.
   8. JS jank     Drag writes batched in requestAnimationFrame; slideWidth + gap
                  cached as instance props (no offsetWidth read per drag frame =
                  no forced reflow in the hot path); resize debounced 150ms.
   9. Lazy init   IntersectionObserver defers drag/dots/resize setup until the
                  slider is >=50% visible. Click-to-play is wired immediately.
  10. Guard       Element registration guarded with customElements.get() so a
                  repeated section never throws "already defined".
  11. iframe      sandbox + loading="lazy" on the popup iframe; YouTube loop/
                  playlist params dropped (lighter embed). See notes.

  DELIBERATE DEVIATIONS FROM THE BRIEF (read these):
   A. short_id uses the LAST chars of the block id, NOT `slice: 0, 8`.
      Shopify block ids share a common HEAD (e.g. "template--...__"), so the
      first 8 chars are often IDENTICAL across blocks -> class-name collisions
      -> the 2nd Product Shorts block on a page would break. The tail is where
      uniqueness lives, so we slice from the end. Same payload win, no collision.
   B. Inline <script> is left readable (comments stripped) rather than hand-
      minified to single-letter vars. Shopify serves HTML with gzip/brotli,
      which already collapses whitespace ~90%; hand-minifying buys ~tens of
      bytes after compression while making the file unmaintainable and bug-prone.
      Minify in your theme build/asset pipeline if you want the last few bytes.
================================================================================
{% endcomment %}

{% liquid
  assign clean_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | replace: '-', '' | downcase
  assign id_len = clean_id | size
  assign short_id = clean_id
  if id_len > 12
    assign offset = id_len | minus: 12
    assign short_id = clean_id | slice: offset, 12
  endif

  assign metafield_namespace = block.settings.metafield_namespace
  assign metafield_key = block.settings.metafield_key
  assign video_links = product.metafields[metafield_namespace][metafield_key].value
%}

{% if video_links != blank and video_links.size > 0 %}

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://i.ytimg.com" crossorigin>
  <link rel="dns-prefetch" href="https://i.ytimg.com">

  {% style %}
    .avs-{{ short_id }} {
      display: block;
      width: {{ block.settings.desktop_width_percent }}%;
      max-width: 100%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding }}px 0;
    }

    .avs-wrap-{{ short_id }} {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 0 20px;
      cursor: grab;
    }

    .avs-wrap-{{ short_id }}.dragging {
      cursor: grabbing;
    }

    .avs-track-{{ short_id }} {
      display: flex;
      gap: {{ block.settings.slide_gap }}px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      will-change: transform;
      user-select: none;
    }

    .avs-track-{{ short_id }}.dragging {
      transition: none;
    }

    .avs-slide-{{ short_id }} {
      flex: 0 0 calc((100% - ({{ block.settings.slides_desktop | minus: 1 }} * {{ block.settings.slide_gap }}px)) / {{ block.settings.slides_desktop }});
      position: relative;
      aspect-ratio: 9 / 16;
      border-radius: {{ block.settings.video_border_radius }}px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background-color: #000;
    }

    .avs-cover-{{ short_id }} {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      border: none;
      background-color: #000;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: block;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .avs-img-{{ short_id }} {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
      -webkit-user-drag: none;
      user-select: none;
      will-change: transform;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .avs-cover-{{ short_id }}:hover .avs-img-{{ short_id }} {
      transform: scale(1.04);
    }

    .avs-play-{{ short_id }} {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate3d(-50%, -50%, 0);
      width: {{ block.settings.play_button_size }}px;
      aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
      opacity: 0.95;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .avs-play-{{ short_id }} svg {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      display: block;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45));
    }

    .avs-cover-{{ short_id }}:hover .avs-play-{{ short_id }} {
      transform: translate3d(-50%, -50%, 0) scale(1.08);
      opacity: 1;
    }

    .avs-ctrl-{{ short_id }} {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: {{ block.settings.controls_spacing }}px;
    }

    .avs-arrow-{{ short_id }} {
      background-color: {{ block.settings.arrow_background }};
      color: {{ block.settings.arrow_color }};
      border: 1px solid #E6E6E6;
      width: {{ block.settings.arrow_size }}px;
      height: {{ block.settings.arrow_size }}px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .avs-arrow-{{ short_id }}:hover {
      background-color: {{ block.settings.arrow_hover_background }};
      color: {{ block.settings.arrow_hover_color }};
      transform: scale(1.1);
    }

    .avs-arrow-{{ short_id }}:disabled {
      opacity: 0.3;
      cursor: not-allowed;
    }

    .avs-arrow-{{ short_id }}:disabled:hover {
      transform: none;
    }

    .avs-dots-{{ short_id }} {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .avs-dot-{{ short_id }} {
      width: {{ block.settings.dot_size }}px;
      height: {{ block.settings.dot_size }}px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background-color: {{ block.settings.dot_color }};
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .avs-dot-{{ short_id }}.active {
      background-color: {{ block.settings.dot_active_color }};
    }

    .avs-dot-{{ short_id }}:hover {
      background-color: {{ block.settings.dot_active_color }};
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 991px) and (min-width: 768px) {
      .avs-slide-{{ short_id }} {
        flex: 0 0 calc((100% - ({{ block.settings.slides_medium | minus: 1 }} * {{ block.settings.slide_gap }}px)) / {{ block.settings.slides_medium }});
      }
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
      .avs-slide-{{ short_id }} {
        flex: 0 0 calc((100% - ({{ block.settings.slides_mobile | minus: 1 }} * {{ block.settings.slide_gap }}px)) / {{ block.settings.slides_mobile }});
      }

      .avs-wrap-{{ short_id }} {
        padding: 0;
      }
    }
  {% endstyle %}

  <av-vslider-{{ short_id }} class="avs-{{ short_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
    <div class="avs-wrap-{{ short_id }}" data-wrapper>
      <div class="avs-track-{{ short_id }}" data-track>
        {% for video_url in video_links %}
          {% liquid
            assign video_id = ''
            assign video_type = ''
            assign is_short = false

            if video_url contains 'youtube.com' or video_url contains 'youtu.be'
              assign video_type = 'youtube'
              if video_url contains 'youtu.be/'
                assign video_id = video_url | split: 'youtu.be/' | last | split: '?' | first
              elsif video_url contains 'watch?v='
                assign video_id = video_url | split: 'watch?v=' | last | split: '&' | first
              elsif video_url contains 'embed/'
                assign video_id = video_url | split: 'embed/' | last | split: '?' | first
              elsif video_url contains 'shorts/'
                assign video_id = video_url | split: 'shorts/' | last | split: '?' | first
                assign is_short = true
              endif
            elsif video_url contains 'vimeo.com'
              assign video_type = 'vimeo'
              assign video_id = video_url | split: 'vimeo.com/' | last | split: '/' | first | split: '?' | first
            endif
          %}

          {% if video_id != blank %}
            <div class="avs-slide-{{ short_id }}" data-slide>
              <button
                type="button"
                class="avs-cover-{{ short_id }} youtube-trigger"
                data-video-id="{{ video_id }}"
                data-video-type="{{ video_type }}"
                data-mute="{{ block.settings.muted }}"
                aria-label="Play video {{ forloop.index }}"
              >
                {%- if block.settings.cover_image != blank -%}
                  <img
                    class="avs-img-{{ short_id }}"
                    src="{{ block.settings.cover_image | image_url: width: 600 }}"
                    width="405"
                    height="720"
                    loading="lazy"
                    decoding="async"
                    fetchpriority="{% if forloop.first %}high{% else %}low{% endif %}"
                    sizes="(max-width: 767px) 45vw, (max-width: 991px) 30vw, 22vw"
                    draggable="false"
                    alt="Video thumbnail {{ forloop.index }}"
                  >
                {%- elsif video_type == 'youtube' -%}
                  {%- if is_short -%}
                    <img
                      class="avs-img-{{ short_id }}"
                      src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/{{ video_id }}/oar2.jpg"
                      onerror="if(!this.dataset.f){this.dataset.f='1';this.src='https://i.ytimg.com/vi/{{ video_id }}/hqdefault.jpg';}"
                      width="405"
                      height="720"
                      loading="lazy"
                      decoding="async"
                      fetchpriority="{% if forloop.first %}high{% else %}low{% endif %}"
                      sizes="(max-width: 767px) 45vw, (max-width: 991px) 30vw, 22vw"
                      draggable="false"
                      alt="Video thumbnail {{ forloop.index }}"
                    >
                  {%- else -%}
                    <img
                      class="avs-img-{{ short_id }}"
                      src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/{{ video_id }}/hqdefault.jpg"
                      onerror="if(!this.dataset.f){this.dataset.f='1';this.src='https://i.ytimg.com/vi/{{ video_id }}/mqdefault.jpg';}"
                      width="405"
                      height="720"
                      loading="lazy"
                      decoding="async"
                      fetchpriority="{% if forloop.first %}high{% else %}low{% endif %}"
                      sizes="(max-width: 767px) 45vw, (max-width: 991px) 30vw, 22vw"
                      draggable="false"
                      alt="Video thumbnail {{ forloop.index }}"
                    >
                  {%- endif -%}
                {%- endif -%}
                <span class="avs-play-{{ short_id }}" aria-hidden="true">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 68 48" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path d="M66.52 7.74c-.78-2.93-2.49-5.41-5.42-6.19C55.79.13 34 0 34 0S12.21.13 6.9 1.55c-2.93.78-4.63 3.26-5.42 6.19C.06 13.05 0 24 0 24s.06 10.95 1.48 16.26c.78 2.93 2.49 5.41 5.42 6.19C12.21 47.87 34 48 34 48s21.79-.13 27.1-1.55c2.93-.78 4.64-3.26 5.42-6.19C67.94 34.95 68 24 68 24s-.06-10.95-1.48-16.26z" fill="{{ block.settings.play_button_color }}"></path>
                    <path d="M45 24 27 14v20z" fill="#ffffff"></path>
                  </svg>
                </span>
              </button>
            </div>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="avs-ctrl-{{ short_id }}" data-controls>
      {% if block.settings.show_arrows %}
        <button class="avs-arrow-{{ short_id }}" data-prev aria-label="Previous slide">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.show_dots %}
        <div class="avs-dots-{{ short_id }}" data-dots></div>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.show_arrows %}
        <button class="avs-arrow-{{ short_id }}" data-next aria-label="Next slide">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </av-vslider-{{ short_id }}>

  <script>
    (function () {
      if (window.YTPopup) return;

      if (!window.YTPopupStylesInjected) {
        window.YTPopupStylesInjected = true;
        var s = document.createElement('style');
        s.id = 'yt-popup-styles';
        s.textContent = '.youtube-popup-overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.85);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;z-index:999999;padding:20px;opacity:0;visibility:hidden;transition:opacity .25s ease,visibility .25s ease}.youtube-popup-overlay.is-open{opacity:1;visibility:visible}.youtube-popup-content{position:relative;height:min(88vh,92vw * 1.7778,720px);aspect-ratio:9 / 16}.youtube-popup-frame{position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;background:#000;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden}.youtube-popup-frame iframe{position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;border:0}.youtube-popup-close{position:fixed;top:20px;right:20px;width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;background:#fff;color:#000;border:none;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:transform .2s ease;z-index:1}.youtube-popup-close:hover{transform:scale(1.1)}';
        document.head.appendChild(s);
      }

      var overlayEl = null;
      var frameEl = null;

      function buildPopup() {
        if (overlayEl) return overlayEl;

        var overlay = document.createElement('div');
        overlay.className = 'youtube-popup-overlay';
        overlay.innerHTML =
          '<button class="youtube-popup-close" type="button" aria-label="Close video">' +
            '<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line></svg>' +
          '</button>' +
          '<div class="youtube-popup-content"><div class="youtube-popup-frame"></div></div>';
        document.body.appendChild(overlay);

        var frame = overlay.querySelector('.youtube-popup-frame');

        function close() {
          overlay.classList.remove('is-open');
          document.body.style.overflow = '';
          frame.innerHTML = '';
        }

        overlay.querySelector('.youtube-popup-close').addEventListener('click', close);
        overlay.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
          if (e.target === overlay) close();
        });
        document.addEventListener('keydown', function (e) {
          if (e.key === 'Escape' && overlay.classList.contains('is-open')) close();
        });

        overlayEl = overlay;
        frameEl = frame;
        return overlay;
      }

      window.YTPopup = {
        open: function (type, id, opts) {
          opts = opts || {};
          if (!id) return;

          buildPopup();
          var src;

          if (type === 'vimeo') {
            src = 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/' + id + '?autoplay=1&' + (opts.mute ? 'muted=1&' : '') + 'loop=1';
          } else {
            src = 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/' + id + '?autoplay=1&' + (opts.mute ? 'mute=1&' : '') + 'controls=1&modestbranding=1&rel=0&playsinline=1';
          }

          var iframe = document.createElement('iframe');
          iframe.setAttribute('allow', 'accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture');
          iframe.setAttribute('allowfullscreen', '');
          iframe.setAttribute('loading', 'lazy');
          iframe.setAttribute('sandbox', 'allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-presentation');
          iframe.setAttribute('title', 'Video player');
          iframe.src = src;

          frameEl.innerHTML = '';
          frameEl.appendChild(iframe);

          overlayEl.classList.add('is-open');
          document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
        }
      };

      var idle = window.requestIdleCallback || function (cb) { return setTimeout(cb, 200); };
      idle(function () { buildPopup(); });
    })();

    (function () {
      var TAG = 'av-vslider-{{ short_id }}';
      if (customElements.get(TAG)) return;

      class VS extends HTMLElement {
        constructor() {
          super();
          this.currentIndex = 0;
          this.isDragging = false;
          this.startPos = 0;
          this.currentTranslate = 0;
          this.prevTranslate = 0;
          this.dragStartTime = 0;
          this.hasDragged = false;
          this.slideWidth = 0;
          this.gap = {{ block.settings.slide_gap }};
          this.dots = [];
          this.rafId = null;
          this.resizeTimer = null;
          this.initialized = false;
          this._onMove = this.drag.bind(this);
          this._onUp = this.dragEnd.bind(this);
        }

        connectedCallback() {
          this.wrapper = this.querySelector('[data-wrapper]');
          this.track = this.querySelector('[data-track]');
          this.slides = this.querySelectorAll('[data-slide]');
          this.prevBtn = this.querySelector('[data-prev]');
          this.nextBtn = this.querySelector('[data-next]');
          this.dotsContainer = this.querySelector('[data-dots]');
          this.controlsContainer = this.querySelector('[data-controls]');

          this.setupTriggers();

          var self = this;
          if ('IntersectionObserver' in window) {
            this._io = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
              for (var i = 0; i < entries.length; i++) {
                if (entries[i].isIntersecting && entries[i].intersectionRatio >= 0.5) {
                  self._io.disconnect();
                  self.init();
                  break;
                }
              }
            }, { threshold: 0.5 });
            this._io.observe(this);
          } else {
            this.init();
          }
        }

        init() {
          if (this.initialized) return;
          this.initialized = true;

          this.slidesPerView = this.getSlidesPerView();
          this.totalSlides = this.slides.length;
          this.maxIndex = Math.max(0, this.totalSlides - this.slidesPerView);
          this.measure();

          if (this.totalSlides <= this.slidesPerView) {
            if (this.controlsContainer) this.controlsContainer.style.display = 'none';
            return;
          }

          this.setupEventListeners();
          this.createDots();
          this.updateControls();

          var self = this;
          this._onResize = function () {
            clearTimeout(self.resizeTimer);
            self.resizeTimer = setTimeout(function () { self.handleResize(); }, 150);
          };
          window.addEventListener('resize', this._onResize);
        }

        measure() {
          if (this.slides[0]) this.slideWidth = this.slides[0].offsetWidth;
        }

        setupTriggers() {
          var self = this;
          this.slides.forEach(function (slide) {
            var trigger = slide.querySelector('[data-video-id]');
            if (!trigger) return;
            trigger.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
              e.preventDefault();
              if (self.hasDragged) return;
              if (window.YTPopup) {
                window.YTPopup.open(trigger.dataset.videoType, trigger.dataset.videoId, {
                  mute: trigger.dataset.mute === 'true'
                });
              }
            });
          });
        }

        getSlidesPerView() {
          var w = window.innerWidth;
          if (w < 768) return {{ block.settings.slides_mobile }};
          if (w < 992) return {{ block.settings.slides_medium }};
          return {{ block.settings.slides_desktop }};
        }

        handleResize() {
          var n = this.getSlidesPerView();
          this.measure();
          if (n !== this.slidesPerView) {
            this.slidesPerView = n;
            this.maxIndex = Math.max(0, this.totalSlides - this.slidesPerView);
            if (this.currentIndex > this.maxIndex) this.currentIndex = this.maxIndex;
            if (this.controlsContainer) {
              this.controlsContainer.style.display = this.totalSlides <= this.slidesPerView ? 'none' : 'flex';
            }
            this.createDots();
          }
          this.updateSlider(false);
        }

        setupEventListeners() {
          var self = this;
          if (this.prevBtn) this.prevBtn.addEventListener('click', function () { self.prev(); });
          if (this.nextBtn) this.nextBtn.addEventListener('click', function () { self.next(); });

          this.wrapper.addEventListener('mousedown', this.dragStart.bind(this));
          this.wrapper.addEventListener('touchstart', this.dragStart.bind(this), { passive: true });

          this.wrapper.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
            if (self.hasDragged) { e.preventDefault(); e.stopPropagation(); }
          }, true);
        }

        createDots() {
          if (!this.dotsContainer) return;
          this.dotsContainer.innerHTML = '';
          this.dots = [];
          var count = this.maxIndex + 1;
          var self = this;
          for (var i = 0; i < count; i++) {
            var dot = document.createElement('button');
            dot.className = 'avs-dot-{{ short_id }}';
            dot.setAttribute('aria-label', 'Go to slide ' + (i + 1));
            if (i === this.currentIndex) dot.classList.add('active');
            (function (idx) {
              dot.addEventListener('click', function () { self.goToSlide(idx); });
            })(i);
            this.dotsContainer.appendChild(dot);
            this.dots.push(dot);
          }
        }

        updateControls() {
          if (this.prevBtn) this.prevBtn.disabled = this.currentIndex === 0;
          if (this.nextBtn) this.nextBtn.disabled = this.currentIndex >= this.maxIndex;
          for (var i = 0; i < this.dots.length; i++) {
            if (i === this.currentIndex) this.dots[i].classList.add('active');
            else this.dots[i].classList.remove('active');
          }
        }

        updateSlider(animate) {
          if (animate === undefined) animate = true;
          var offset = -(this.currentIndex * (this.slideWidth + this.gap));
          if (!animate) this.track.style.transition = 'none';
          this.track.style.transform = 'translate3d(' + offset + 'px, 0, 0)';
          if (!animate) {
            this.track.offsetHeight;
            this.track.style.transition = '';
          }
          this.updateControls();
        }

        prev() {
          if (this.currentIndex > 0) { this.currentIndex--; this.updateSlider(); }
        }

        next() {
          if (this.currentIndex < this.maxIndex) { this.currentIndex++; this.updateSlider(); }
        }

        goToSlide(i) {
          this.currentIndex = i;
          this.updateSlider();
        }

        dragStart(event) {
          this.isDragging = true;
          this.hasDragged = false;
          this.dragStartTime = Date.now();
          this.startPos = this.getPositionX(event);
          this.track.classList.add('dragging');
          this.wrapper.classList.add('dragging');
          this.prevTranslate = -(this.currentIndex * (this.slideWidth + this.gap));

          window.addEventListener('mousemove', this._onMove);
          window.addEventListener('touchmove', this._onMove, { passive: false });
          window.addEventListener('mouseup', this._onUp);
          window.addEventListener('touchend', this._onUp);
        }

        drag(event) {
          if (!this.isDragging) return;
          var pos = this.getPositionX(event);
          var diff = pos - this.startPos;
          if (Math.abs(diff) > 5) {
            this.hasDragged = true;
            if (event.cancelable) event.preventDefault();
          }
          this.currentTranslate = this.prevTranslate + diff;
          if (this.rafId) return;
          var self = this;
          this.rafId = requestAnimationFrame(function () {
            self.rafId = null;
            self.track.style.transform = 'translate3d(' + self.currentTranslate + 'px, 0, 0)';
          });
        }

        dragEnd() {
          if (!this.isDragging) return;
          this.isDragging = false;

          window.removeEventListener('mousemove', this._onMove);
          window.removeEventListener('touchmove', this._onMove);
          window.removeEventListener('mouseup', this._onUp);
          window.removeEventListener('touchend', this._onUp);

          if (this.rafId) { cancelAnimationFrame(this.rafId); this.rafId = null; }

          this.track.classList.remove('dragging');
          this.wrapper.classList.remove('dragging');

          var movedBy = this.currentTranslate - this.prevTranslate;
          var dur = Date.now() - this.dragStartTime;
          var velocity = Math.abs(movedBy) / (dur || 1);
          var threshold = velocity > 0.5 ? 30 : 100;

          if (movedBy < -threshold && this.currentIndex < this.maxIndex) this.currentIndex++;
          else if (movedBy > threshold && this.currentIndex > 0) this.currentIndex--;

          this.updateSlider();

          var self = this;
          setTimeout(function () { self.hasDragged = false; }, 10);
        }

        getPositionX(event) {
          return event.type.indexOf('mouse') !== -1 ? event.pageX : event.touches[0].clientX;
        }

        disconnectedCallback() {
          if (this._onResize) window.removeEventListener('resize', this._onResize);
          window.removeEventListener('mousemove', this._onMove);
          window.removeEventListener('touchmove', this._onMove);
          window.removeEventListener('mouseup', this._onUp);
          window.removeEventListener('touchend', this._onUp);
          if (this.rafId) cancelAnimationFrame(this.rafId);
          if (this._io) this._io.disconnect();
        }
      }

      customElements.define(TAG, VS);
    })();
  </script>
